@AgentApi = http://localhost:5010

### List Dispatches Filtered By Related Entity
GET {{AgentApi}}/dispatches/filtered?relatedEntityId=c394835f-ce35-4e6b-8cd7-7e553def2e25
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Dispatch
POST {{AgentApi}}/dispatches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Unauthorized aircraft detected",
  "description": "Unidentified aircraft entered restricted airspace in sector north east.",
  "category": 1,
  "occuredAt": "2026-06-10T08:00:00Z",
  "relatedEntityId": "c394835f-ce35-4e6b-8cd7-7e553def2e25",
  "relatedChildEntityId": null
}

###

### Update Dispatch
PUT {{AgentApi}}/dispatches/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Unauthorized aircraft detected — updated",
  "description": "Unidentified aircraft intercepted and identified as friendly.",
  "category": 1,
  "occuredAt": "2026-06-10T08:30:00Z",
  "relatedEntityId": "c394835f-ce35-4e6b-8cd7-7e553def2e25",
  "relatedChildEntityId": null
}

###

### Delete Dispatch
DELETE {{AgentApi}}/dispatches/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

